metadata.name: Caipirinha Capim Santo
metadata.description:
A symbol of Brazilianness, caipirinha is a drink traditionally made with lemon, sugar and cachaça. But there are many adaptations with a wide variety of fruits and herbs that can be used.
This is a delicious variation made with lemon and lemongrass stalk.

Artist: Stela Narayana
Edition: 1/1
Dimensions: 2848 × 2649px
Location: Trancoso, Bahia / Brazil
Photo taken Sept 2021
